{"about_the_game":"<strong><i>\u201cGolfie is Slay the Spire meets Golf With Your Friends\u201d</i> - Lewis Brindley, Yogscast.</strong><br><br>Golfie is a roguelike, deckbuilding minigolf game for 1-8 players. Each run requires strategy, planning, and skill. Build unique decks which will unlock incredible new ways to play, giving you the power to pull off some spectacular shots - or die trying.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579020/extras/Multishots_616.gif?t=1726160755\" /><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">GOLFIE WITH YOUR FRIENDS</h2></strong><br>Join your friends in the action-packed, chaotic multiplayer mode and pitch your wits, skills and devious use of cards against your opponents.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579020/extras/Multiplayer_1.gif?t=1726160755\" /><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">SLAY THE GREEN</h2></strong><br>Set off from the clubhouse in procedurally-generated roguelike single-player, building upon an ever expanding deck of cards to modify your shots and conquer the 18 holes.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579020/extras/RLikeSmol.jpg?t=1726160755\" /><br><br>Card powers can vary from increasing the distance or elevation of a standard shot, through to out-of-this-world abilities and power-ups which can be combined to dazzling effect. But be careful: finish over par and you\u2019ll lose some energy \u2013 and once it\u2019s totally depleted, the run is over. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579020/extras/Inflate_616.gif?t=1726160755\" /><br><br>Daily runs, endless modes and seeded runs mean you\u2019ll never run out of holes to play. Gain experience during each run to unlock an ever-increasing pool of cards and customisation options, then return to the course with even more ways to play.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579020/extras/combo_918.gif?t=1726160755\" /><br><br>With the full release of Golfie you can now take to the fairway with your friends in a no holds barred battle for Golfie supremacy. Earn points by racing to be first to the hole, collect all the coins and crystals, or use your power-ups to ensure that only you make it to the hole to secure your victory at the top of the leaderboard. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579020/extras/Multiplayer_2.gif?t=1726160755\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Hole in one!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1579020/89427c7c489b12e8270815877171c425a21cd05f.jpg"},{"name":"Hole in... None?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1579020/e4dc09aacc82d91732e5ecbc18299c87c2fcf1e9.jpg"},{"name":"Cheater","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1579020/ec94ad46200a3c9c8871317b1e42eddab9d1ef81.jpg"},{"name":"Go Big or Go Home","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1579020/f1d9edc9ab966eb641552e23df877631da3b441f.jpg"},{"name":"Dress Up","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1579020/d751682bca5df1fdf123ab151dbe1d897cbf3872.jpg"},{"name":"Wealthy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1579020/bbe4316c4cb39cace95fe0c5cacc90c7a0ff8760.jpg"},{"name":"Archnemesis","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1579020/6783f169fa929665d496c715d3422255e43f0ab0.jpg"},{"name":"Challenger","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1579020/251e9c155f648d8100ad2de4040cfd76a69dee57.jpg"},{"name":"Shopping Spree","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamco